summary: Adds more time to do the 5 sticks riddle (Enderal)
descriptionHtml:
This is a very small mod for Enderal, which adds more time to do the 5 sticks riddle. If you don't know what I'm talking about, just ignore this, you either aren't there yet or it was easy enough for you and you already forgot about it.
I added 18 seconds to the previous 12 for a total of 30 seconds to complete the task. Now you could do it by walking.
Most people won't need it at all, but if you are like me and both hate those type of challenges and are truly bad at them, you might wish to give it a try to save yourself some frustration.

Since the script seems to be only for this part of the quest, nothing else shoud be broken or affected in any way.

To install, just extract it in the Data folder. You can simply delete it afterwards.
author: JasmineMcCoy
